item.title: CVE-2020-6187|2024-08-04T08:55:21.848Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20%28guided%20procedures%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver (Guided Procedures), versions 7.10, 7.11, 7.20, 7.30, 7.31, 7.40, 7.50, does not sufficiently validate an XML document input from a compromised admin, leading to Denial of Service.
